sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant FE as 前端 MessageCenter
    participant WS as ChatWebSocket
    participant MG as MongoDB
    participant API as HTTP /api/message/read
    participant MySQL as MySQL
    participant Redis as Redis

    U->>FE: 点击会话
    FE->>WS: connectWebSocket(conversationId)
    WS->>MG: getHistory(conversationId)
    WS-->>FE: {type:"history", messages:[...]}
    FE->>API: markAsRead(senderId)
    API->>MySQL: 批量更新 isRead=1
    API->>Redis: 未读数 -N
    FE->>FE: fetchUnreadCount() 刷新红点
